data.description: PRIME location!! Come fall in love with this stylish ranch home nestled on a quiet street with NO HOA. The single level 3 bedroom, 2 bath remodeled home with pool on a corner lot is a perfect income property or family home. The bright Living Room welcomes you in the front door just steps away from the formal dining room for perfect entertaining. The Kitchen is both spacious and beautiful featuring all of the amenities of a true chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, farm sink, smooth cooktop, white cabinetry, peninsula with breakfast bar and breakfast room. The family room is steps from the kitchen with a cozy fireplace and French doors leading to an extended covered patio in this entertainer's dream backyard with pool. The mature landscaping and putting green is perfect for enjoying Arizona evenings. A HUGE backyard for the kids and 4-legged family members to play. World class shopping, restaurants, museums and nightlife right outside your doorstep! Plus quick access to freeways for easy commuting.
